com.i2group.apollo.cqrs

Interface IEvent

  • All Known Subinterfaces:
    IDataSourceEvent, IDataSourceSchemaEvent, IDataSourceSecuritySchemaEvent
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    CardAddedToItemEvent, CardAmendedEvent, CardDeletedFromItemEvent, DataSourceCreatedEvent, DataSourceSchemaAmendedEvent, EntityCreatedEvent, EntityMergedEvent, EntitySupplantedEvent, Event, ItemDeletedEvent, ItemPurgedEvent, LinkAmendedEvent, LinkCreatedEvent, PrimaryPropertiesChangedEvent, SecurityPermissionChangeEvent, SecuritySchemaAmendedEvent, SecuritySchemaCreatedEvent, SetAmendedEvent

    public interface IEvent
    An event that was generated during command processing and placed into the event store.
    Since:
    2.0

    • Method Summary

      All Methods Instance Methods Abstract Methods 
      Modifier and Type Method and Description
      String getComment()
      Gets a String containing the comment associated with this IEvent.
      ItemIdentifierAndVersion getItemIdentifierAndVersion()
      Gets the ItemIdentifierAndVersion of the Item to which this IEvent applies.
      String getOriginatingAddress()
      Gets a String containing the originating address of the command that caused this IEvent.
      Long getSequenceNumber()
      Gets the sequence number of this IEvent.
      String getSourcePrincipalName()
      Gets a String containing the name of the principal who executed the command that caused this IEvent.
      XMLGregorianCalendar getTimestamp()
      Gets an XMLGregorianCalendar containing the time stamp for this IEvent.
